title: Vanilla Pizzelles using the Cuisinart International Chef™
description: Cuisinart is creating international buzz with its new International Chef™ Crêpe/Pizzelle/Pancake Plus! This multicultural countertop press makes crêpes, tortillas, blintzes, pizzelles, and more. Opened flat, it turns into a griddle for traditional or Swedish pancakes. Reversible, nonstick plates are dishwasher safe. Indicator lights, adjustable temperature control and timer ensure everything cooks perfectly, and recipes are included from around the world!
